For this reason, then, the Spaniards will bring action before the King, if Princes owe security under the common law to everybody in their realms. Furthermore, our King owes it to the Spaniards under the special legal right which the recent peace established. In the case before us the Spaniards have been wronged by being attacked off the harbor; in the case before us they are suffering injury by being block- aded in the harbor.
